<seg id="1169"> Have become, with very few exceptions, public goods. </seg>
<seg id="1170"> Although the exact terms of the contract </seg>
<seg id="1171"> With the new government have never been made public, </seg>
<seg id="1172"> The outcome is obvious to all: </seg>
<seg id="1173"> Zero Moustafa poured a huge fortune </seg>
<seg id="1174"> In exchange for a costly, unprofitable, decadent hotel. </seg>
<seg id="1175"> Because? </seg>
<seg id="1176"> A mere matter of sentimentality? </seg>
<seg id="1177"> It was not from me, it was not for nothing, </seg>
<seg id="1178"> But I felt I had to know, </seg>
<seg id="1179"> For my health, I believe. </seg>
<seg id="1180"> Forgive me if I asked. I hope I have not offended her. </seg>
<seg id="1181"> Of course not. </seg>
<seg id="1182"> Is that the last link with that vanished world? </seg>
<seg id="1183"> His world, if he wants to? </seg>
