<seg id="1188"> No, I kept the hotel for Agatha. </seg>
<seg id="1189"> We were happy here. </seg>
<seg id="1190"> For a while'. </seg>
<seg id="1191"> To be honest, I believe his world has vanished </seg>
<seg id="1192"> Long before he came in. </seg>
<seg id="1193"> But, I must say, </seg>
