<seg id="1195"> - Salt? - No, I'll sit here for a while. </seg>
<seg id="1196"> Good night, then. </seg>
<seg id="1197"> Next week, </seg>
<seg id="1198"> I went to go and treat myself to South America </seg>
<seg id="1199"> And I started a long wander abroad. </seg>
